{"id":74259,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/真的震撼了我的心——中国，请你诚实！（图）/","date":"2010-05-23T10:50:12Z","modified":"2010-05-23T19:42:13Z","title":"真的震撼了我的心——中国，请你诚实！（图）","content":"<p>中国，请你诚实！！大家尽量转载，让更多人知道。</p>\n<p>这就是我们社会的无奈，有些东西可能有些偏激，但大多数都是事实，中国要发展，要敢于面对事实。</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>悍马和校车相撞，校车怎么可能那么结实？怎么可能？不 是悍马质量差而是校车防护太强了！真的敬佩国外的设计理念！</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/500_510e83ec-96b5-4760-95a8-897c0f824aaf.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74368\" title=\"500_510e83ec-96b5-4760-95a8-897c0f824aaf\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/500_510e83ec-96b5-4760-95a8-897c0f824aaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"515\" height=\"347\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>世博会<br />\n歌舞升平平息不了西南人民的怨气。<br />\n世博投资4000亿，西南大旱救灾1.55亿！ 鲜明的对比~!<br />\n咳咳，我爱祖国！<br />\n我说能把上海的市长送到灾区一阵试试贫民生活么？</strong></span></p>\n<div id=\"xndiv0\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414635515.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74370\" title=\"1273414635515\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414635515.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"350\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://passport.mop.com/xtest/entrance.jsp?succUrl=http://dzh.mop.com/topic/readSub_11539799_0_0.html\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>铁铲是新的，都是全新的，做个秀容易么？钱都是这样用的？</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414706828.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74371\" title=\"1273414706828\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414706828.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" /></a></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>老师教育我们：要透过现象看本质<br />\n我看到的现象：1 我们的建筑物被破坏程度比智力的严重的多<br />\n2 智力地震的级数比我们的大 得到的本质</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414774246.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74372\" title=\"1273414774246\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414774246.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"615\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\">拆迁大队竟然组织了防暴队来阻 止钉子户，并强行拆楼。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414823258.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74373\" title=\"1273414823258\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414823258.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"498\" height=\"332\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>全国有7亿这样的人~他们在为 父母妻儿奋斗~我们能为他做些什么？提供些什么福利保障？？</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414873619.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74374\" title=\"1273414873619\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414873619.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"478\" height=\"407\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414906695.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74375\" title=\"1273414906695\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414906695.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"457\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\">没想到总理也这么敢说</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414963991.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74376\" title=\"1273414963991\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273414963991.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"484\" height=\"178\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\">为人民服务那五个字真是鲜艳啊！！可是到底又服务了谁呢？？人民吗？我看不是。。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415009180.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74377\" title=\"1273415009180\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415009180.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"367\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\">你早上起床尿裤子了，大前天说过的话，怎么说变就变，不懂的话，回去研究几年《易经》。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415073302.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74378\" title=\"1273415073302\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415073302.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"491\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\">真的很淡定，我记得好像看到一则新闻是学生被老师半夜罚站，第二天死在水沟边。校方称那个孩子死得很舒坦。 天呐，还有这样的事。那你怎么不去舒坦的死。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415149991.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74379\" title=\"1273415149991\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415149991.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"167\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\">各种离奇死亡，杀人偿命，真理何在？谁能还事实一个公道？</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415201691.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74380\" title=\"1273415201691\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415201691.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"396\" height=\"800\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>为了炫耀富足，隋炀帝请西域各族首领来洛阳观看百戏演出。各族首领请求允许西域商人入洛阳做买卖，隋炀帝答应了，忙令人装饰洛阳市 容。城内外的树木都用丝帛缠绕，商人必须穿华丽的衣服，甚至卖菜的也要用精美的草席铺地。西域商人路过酒店饭馆，店主要热情邀请他们入座，醉饱出门，不许 收取分文，还要说：“中国丰饶，酒饭一律不要钱.”<br />\n我想起来了一句话：花人民的钱，让他们都去死吧。</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415634433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74381\" title=\"1273415634433\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415634433.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"518\" height=\"351\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>世博园庆典广场，喷雾系统制造出一个如梦如幻的意境（3月31日摄）。4月1日，上海世博会将迎来开幕倒计时30天，目前，世博园 区内各项建设已进入尾声，近万名工人正加班加点，确保 4月下旬世博园区如期投入试运营。新华社记者 任珑摄<br />\n隋炀帝的虚荣浮夸，并不能瞒骗远方的客人，有的提出疑问：“贵国也有穷人，衣不蔽体，为何不用丝帛给他们做衣服，而却用来缠树呢？”</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415686057.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74382\" title=\"1273415686057\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415686057.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"351\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>这不是在庆祝国庆，而是在抵抗 狗R的拆迁队<br />\n爱国之心是怎样被zf泯灭的……我的祖国</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415748835.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74383\" title=\"1273415748835\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415748835.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"367\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\">真正的暴力执法，真正的没有人权，为什么没人问津？是没有利益关系还是小人物不值得注意。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415857720.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74384\" title=\"1273415857720\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273415857720.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"524\" height=\"409\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>中国最高河蟹榜</strong></span></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/20880719_13279055.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74385\" title=\"20880719_13279055\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/20880719_13279055.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"478\" height=\"515\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>记得某吧看到有人呼吁给城市管理者配备武器提高待遇…列举出XX城市城市管理者被打，XX城市管理者工作辛苦。</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416057693.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74386\" title=\"1273416057693\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416057693.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"653\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>【云南】3月7日，云南曲靖市会泽县马路乡岔河村村民丁朝科和女儿背水回家。“我们要去几公里外山脚的江边背水，每天背三趟，不然 牲口都喂不活了。”村民丁朝科说。目前全村40多户 143名村民已经靠背水生活近三个月了，由于交通不便，大型送水车辆根本无法抵达村寨。<br />\n在此，本人呼吁解放军出动解决问题。人民的军队呢</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416115648.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74387\" title=\"1273416115648\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416115648.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"430\" height=\"627\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>广西东兰县兰木乡弄台村，因为路没修通，送水车无法到达更近的位置，这些七八十岁的老人不得不每天往返12-24公里的山路。见到 记者后，14名一起前往挑水的老人跪在路上，请政灬府尽快把路修好，而5年前他们就交了修路的集资款 出自 网易新闻</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416356687.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74388\" title=\"1273416356687\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416356687.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"476\" height=\"309\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>纵横<span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>九万里四海同唱发展歌，祝祖国越来越强盛.人们生活的更有尊严更幸福。<br />\n这张图片的侧面图也是人人网最近搞的一个活动的主要图片，看了很心疼</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416413898.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74389\" title=\"1273416413898\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416413898.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"510\" height=\"339\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>老奶奶只为了能够喝上那么一点水，可怜那水是干净的么？？</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416462870.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74390\" title=\"1273416462870\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416462870.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"468\" height=\"305\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416580263.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74391\" title=\"1273416580263\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416580263.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"295\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416583123.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74392\" title=\"1273416583123\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416583123.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"457\" height=\"303\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416582813.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74394\" title=\"1273416582813\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416582813.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"504\" height=\"590\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416575403.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74395\" title=\"1273416575403\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416575403.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"493\" height=\"339\" /></a></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>多少年了，多少年了，真正的解决了么？有个专家说在2020年会彻底解决，这10年怎么办？</strong></span></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416692507.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74396\" title=\"1273416692507\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416692507.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"497\" height=\"600\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416781024.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74397\" title=\"1273416781024\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416781024.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"474\" height=\"469\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416886351.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74398\" title=\"1273416886351\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416886351.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"596\" height=\"343\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>中国城市管理者真强大，怎么不早出生70年啊。</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416989676.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74399\" title=\"1273416989676\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273416989676.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"398\" height=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417092248.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74400\" title=\"1273417092248\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417092248.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"481\" height=\"380\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417096783.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74401\" title=\"1273417096783\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417096783.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"424\" height=\"308\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>水桶是空的，演员是临时雇来的。<br />\n仅仅两桶水得压垮多少官员？<br />\n</strong></span> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417159529.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74402\" title=\"1273417159529\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417159529.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"473\" height=\"336\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>赞一个，铁腕政策，贪官污吏闻风丧胆。<br />\n不要说他没有实现中国的民主，他没这个能力，他已经尽力了。<br />\n专政国家里治国的根本在于治吏，吏治则民自安。不整治贪官污吏做什么都是在表演。<br />\n虽然我知道现在的国情是不能在这么硬了，但是不能总是这么软吧.</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417188253.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74403\" title=\"1273417188253\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417188253.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"593\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>“我孙文此生啊，没有别的希望，就一个希望，那就是让共和不仅是一个名词，一句空话，或一个形式，要让它成为我们实实在在的生活方 式，让它成为我们牢不可破的信念。共和，是普天之下民众的选择，是世界的潮流。世界潮流浩浩荡荡，顺之者昌，逆之者亡。我孙文相信，我们这个中华民族啊， 它一定会实现共和的！我坚信这一点！”<br />\n国父</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417231374.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74404\" title=\"1273417231374\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/1273417231374.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"519\" height=\"389\" /></a></div>\n","author":952,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9390,10367,8819,9171]}